{"tha-ap324:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap324:0.2":"Umapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap324:0.3":"2 Pulinapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap324:1.1":"“Kakudham vilasantamva, ","tha-ap324:1.2":"nisabhajaniyam yatha; ","tha-ap324:1.3":"Osadhimva virocantam, ","tha-ap324:1.4":"obhasantam narasabham. ","tha-ap324:2.1":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap324:2.2":"avandim satthuno aham; ","tha-ap324:2.3":"Sattharam parivannesim, ","tha-ap324:2.4":"sakakammena tosayim. ","tha-ap324:3.1":"Susuddham pulinam gayha, ","tha-ap324:3.2":"gatamagge samokirim; ","tha-ap324:3.3":"Ucchangena gahetvana, ","tha-ap324:3.4":"vipassissa mahesino. ","tha-ap324:4.1":"Tato upaddhapulinam, ","tha-ap324:4.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","tha-ap324:4.3":"Divavihare osincim, ","tha-ap324:4.4":"dvipadindassa tadino. ","tha-ap324:5.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap324:5.2":"pulinam yamasincaham; ","tha-ap324:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap324:5.4":"pulinassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap324:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap324:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap324:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap324:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pulinapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap324:8.1":"Pulinapujakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}